sourcesContent: import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { Router } from '@angular/router'; import { CookieService } from 'ngx-cookie-service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-toolbar-navigation', templateUrl: './toolbar-navigation.component.html', styleUrls: [], }) export class ToolbarNavigationComponent { constructor(private cookie: CookieService, private router: Router) {} handleLogout(): void { this.cookie.delete('USER_INFO'); void this.router.navigate(['/home']); } }
